frames.caption: A young woman stands on a beach at sunset, gazing over her shoulder towards the camera. The sun casts a warm glow over the ocean, highlighting her light blue outfit and flowing hair.
frames.description: The scene captures a serene moment at the beach during sunset, with a focus on a woman enjoying the tranquil setting. The ocean waves gently lap at the shore, and the sky is painted with hues of orange and blue.

frames.caption: A young woman stands on a beach at sunset, her hair gently blowing in the breeze. Behind her, a large whale breaches dramatically from the ocean, creating a splash against the backdrop of a colorful sky.
frames.description: The scene captures a serene beach setting during sunset, with a young woman in the foreground and a whale breaching in the background. The juxtaposition of the calm human presence and the dynamic ocean life creates a striking visual contrast.
